Package: hysteria
Version: __VERSION__
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Kotodian fork <noreply@github.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/Kotodian/hysteria
Description: Hysteria 2 QUIC-based TCP & UDP proxy (Kotodian fork)
 Hysteria is a powerful, lightning fast and censorship resistant proxy.
 This package ships the hysteria binary and a systemd unit for running
 the server. Kotodian fork adds configurable initialPacketSize and a
 disconnect webhook logger on top of upstream apernet/hysteria.
